Revision history for Dist-Zilla-Plugin-PerlTidy

0.17    2014-10-03
        Fix to prevent certain Perl files from being skipped (by Steven Lee)

0.16    2014-03-21
        do not try to read binary file

0.15    2014-01-22
        fix tests

0.14    2014.01.04
        command perltidy ignoring .build and Module-VERSION (RT 91288, patches from KENTNL)

0.13    2012.02.22
        Add support for alternative tidy backends (Kent Fredric)
        Fix the excessive production of *.LOG files (Kent Fredric)

0.12    2011.08.04
        Permit 'dzil perltidy' to work without any configuration at all - kentnl

        Permit '[PerlTidy]' to omit a configuration file path and defer to default - kentnl

        Add notices about '~' and co not being expanded in configuration paths - kentnl

        Misc distribution fixes - kentnl

        Added minor behaviour tests - kentnl

0.11    2011.07.21
        reverting to previous patch - ignoring FromCode (Alexei (RUSSOZ))

0.10    2011.07.20
        fixes for ref($file) eq 'Dist::Zilla::File::FromCode' (Alexei (RUSSOZ))

0.09    2010.06.03
	    perltidyrc is now resolved using Perl::Tidy defaults if not
	    specified (robinsmidsrod)

0.08_01 2010.03.31
        fix for Dist::Zilla 2's removal of dzil_app (gardnerm)
        additional POD (gardnerm)

